    },
    "body": "Per [BIP327](https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0327.mediawiki?plain=1#L300), MuSig2 key aggregation is defined for `u` public keys where `0 < u < 2^32`.\r\n\r\nPreviously, the code did not handle `u == 0`.\r\n\r\nThis patch updates the code to reject an empty pubkey list and adds a regression test.",
